@startuml edit-date
title Edit Date User Flow

actor User
participant "Date List" as List
participant "Date Detail" as Detail
participant "Edit Modal" as Modal
participant "API" as API
participant "Database" as DB

User -> List: View date list
User -> List: Click on date entry
List -> Detail: Navigate to date detail

Detail -> API: GET /api/dates/{dateId}
API -> DB: Fetch date record
DB --> API: Return date data
API --> Detail: Return date details
Detail -> User: Display date information

User -> Detail: Click "Edit" button
Detail -> Modal: Open edit modal\n(pre-populated with data)
Modal -> User: Display editable form

User -> Modal: Modify date fields\n(Name, Date, Type, Notes)
User -> Modal: Click "Save"

Modal -> API: PUT /api/dates/{dateId}
API -> DB: Update date record
DB --> API: Confirm update
API --> Modal: Return success

Modal -> User: Show success notification
Modal -> Detail: Close modal & refresh
Detail -> User: Display updated date

@enduml
